--><h2>Reading raw picture<a name="1"></a></h2>

<h2>Creating mask to cut out profile<a name="2"></a></h2>
{% highlight matlab %}

ch1=double(RAW(:,:,1))./255;
ch2=double(RAW(:,:,2))./255;
ch3=double(RAW(:,:,3))./255;

fc=[0 0 1];
x=[0 0 0 0 2 -1];

%b=(fc(1).*(ch1.^x(1)))+(fc(2).*(ch2.^x(2)))+fc(3).*(ch3.^x(3));

BW=(fc(1).*ch1.*(ch2.^x(1)).*(ch2.^x(2)))+(fc(2).*ch2.*(ch1.^x(3)).*(ch3.^x(4)))+(fc(3).*ch3.*(ch1.^x(5)).*(ch2.^x(6)));
BW(isnan(BW))=0;
BW(isinf(BW))=0;
BW=double((BW./max(BW))&lt;0.5);

imagesc(BW);colormap(gray)

{% endhighlight %}

<img src="data:image/png;base64," />
<h2>Select outer border<a name="3"></a></h2>
{% highlight matlab %}

PROFILE = BW+BW(:,[2:end end])+BW(:,[1 1:end-1])+BW([1 1:end-1],:)+BW([2:end end],:);
PROFILE(PROFILE==max(max(PROFILE)))=0;
imagesc(PROFILE);colormap(gray)

{% endhighlight %}

<img src="data:image/png;base64," />
<h2>Convert outer border pixel to xy-position<a name="4"></a></h2>
{% highlight matlab %}

[x,y]=meshgrid(1:size(PROFILE,2),1:size(PROFILE,1));
xy=[x(PROFILE&gt;0) y(PROFILE&gt;0)];
xy(:,2)=0-xy(:,2);
plot(xy(:,1),xy(:,2),'.');
axis off;

{% endhighlight %}

<img src="data:image/png;base64," />
<h2>Add noise to xy coordinates<a name="5"></a></h2>
{% highlight matlab %}

noise=2.*[1 1.5 1.8 2].^10;
for i=1:4
    subplot(2,2,i)
    scatter(xy(:,1)+noise(i).*rand(size(xy,1),1),xy(:,2)+noise(i).*rand(size(xy,1),1),'.');axis off;
    title(['noise = ',num2str(noise(i))],'color','r')
end

{% endhighlight %}

<img src="data:image/png;base64," />
<h2>Generate gif<a name="6"></a></h2>
{% highlight matlab %}

noise=2.*[0:0.1:2 2:-0.1:0].^10;
h=figure;
for i=1:length(noise)
    scatter(xy(:,1)+noise(i).*rand(size(xy,1),1),xy(:,2)+noise(i).*rand(size(xy,1),1),0.2,'.w');axis off;set(gcf,'color','k')
    frame = getframe(h);
    im = frame2im(frame);
    im=im(:,:,1)&gt;0;
if i==1
        imwrite(im,'test.gif','gif', 'Loopcount',inf,'delaytime',0.05);
else
        imwrite(im,'test.gif','gif', 'WriteMode','append','delaytime',0.05);
end
end
